    {
      "id": "78ed4419-d2c4-4c32-9524-5d8b59f7075c",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "To address this gap, authors propose a day-wise model to predict performance called ANN-LSTM. Model was compared against a baseline RNN and baseline GRU model. Moreover, results were compared against other state-of-the-art methods. During model testing, it was found that, by the 3rd month of a course, ANN-LSTM obliterated the baselines, achieving 70% accuracy in comparison with the 53% and 56% of RNN and GRU.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "78ed4419-d2c4-4c32-9524-5d8b59f7075c",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
          "page_id": "ce7c642e-062c-424b-bf37-b4c7ab778cc4"
        },
        "created_time": "2024-08-06T14:14:00.000Z",
        "last_edited_time": "2024-08-06T14:16:00.000Z",
