            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": {
                "content": "To address this gap, authors propose a day-wise model to predict performance called ANN-LSTM. Model was compared against a baseline RNN and baseline GRU model. Moreover, results were compared against other state-of-the-art methods. During model testing, it was found that, by the 3rd month of a course, ANN-LSTM obliterated the baselines, achieving 70% accuracy in comparison with the 53% and 56% of RNN and GRU.",
                "link": null
